 {
  "i": 23,
  "style": "Title",
  "name": "",
  "text": "{\\fad(2000,0)}Morning Comes!\\NThe Straw Hats' Ultimate Attack!"
 },
 {
  "i": 24,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Amazing, Straw Hat!"
 },
 {
  "i": 25,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "You defeated Oars!"
 },
 {
  "i": 26,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Hey, Luffy! Hang in there!"
 },
 {
  "i": 27,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 28,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We pushed him this far... Is he gonna be alright?"
 },
 {
  "i": 29,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "He must be completely worn out."
 },
 {
  "i": 30,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "He was using the strength of 100 men in a single body."
 },
 {
  "i": 31,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Anyway, we gotta recover the shadows of all the victims quickly!"
 },
 {
  "i": 32,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "That's right!"
 },
 {
  "i": 33,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Let's hurry!"
 },
 {
  "i": 34,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "The sky is getting brighter in the east."
 },
 {
  "i": 35,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It'll be morning any time now."
 },
 {
  "i": 36,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "By the way, how do you get the shadows back?"
 },
 {
  "i": 37,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "4 of our friends were stripped off their shadows too."
 },
 {
  "i": 38,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "That's another problem."
 },
 {
  "i": 39,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "To tell you the truth, we wanted\\NStraw Hat to do that for us, but..."
 },
 {
  "i": 40,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "That'd be impossible, he can't even move right now."
 },
 {
  "i": 41,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Only Moriah, the master of all the shadows the zombies possess, is able to do that."
 },
 {
  "i": 42,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Unless he gives the \"go back to your original master\" order, the shadows won't return."
 },
 {
  "i": 43,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Let's quit the chit-chat and do it."
 },
 {
  "i": 44,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "That's right!"
 },
 {
  "i": 45,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We'll wake Moriah and force him to give the order."
 },
 {
  "i": 46,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "If we don't recover the shadows, then there was no point in beating him!"
 },
 {
  "i": 47,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "O-Oars is back on his feet!"
 },
 {
  "i": 48,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "I thought that attack alone was enough to leave him unconscious!"
 },
 {
  "i": 49,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "This is terrible..."
 },
 {
  "i": 50,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It's all over."
 },
 {
  "i": 51,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "The entire Straw Hat crew is unconscious right now."
 },
 {
  "i": 52,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We've already used all the shadows we had."
 },
 {
  "i": 53,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We don't have anything left to defeat him with."
 },
 {
  "i": 54,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "It doesn't hurt at all."
 },
 {
  "i": 55,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Damn it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 56,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It seems we were no match for the power of a zombie after all!"
 },
 {
  "i": 57,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We have no time left."
 },
 {
  "i": 58,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Dawn is almost upon us."
 },
 {
  "i": 59,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We'll never be freed from dwelling in darkness!"
 },
 {
  "i": 60,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Let's give up."
 },
 {
  "i": 61,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We'll only find death if we stay here."
 },
 {
  "i": 62,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Let's go back to the forest."
 },
 {
  "i": 63,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Let's return... to that gloomy forest where no light can be seen."
 },
 {
  "i": 64,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "You!"
 },
 {
  "i": 65,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "I don't know what happened to Luffy, but..."
 },
 {
  "i": 66,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "We have the upper hand right now."
 },
 {
  "i": 67,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "H-Hey! Wait a minute, you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 68,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "If you move in that state you'll die!"
 },
 {
  "i": 69,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "He received the attack of that monster... How come he's still standing?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 70,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "I can't tell which one is the zombie here!"
 },
 {
  "i": 71,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Hey, where did the Straw Hats we rescued go?"
 },
 {
  "i": 72,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Don't ask me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 73,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "They couldn't have moved while being unconscious!"
 },
 {
  "i": 74,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Huh, where are the other two?"
 },
 {
  "i": 75,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Y-You're right!"
 },
 {
  "i": 76,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "The Long-nose and the woman are both gone."
 },
 {
  "i": 77,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Did they... go ahead and run off?"
 },
 {
  "i": 78,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Huh, all of them?!"
