  "i": 168,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "If it's straightened out, the force isn't migitated, and all the damage is taken."
 },
 {
  "i": 169,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Go, Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 170,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Good luck to you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 171,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I'll give you an extra-large bazooka!"
 },
 {
  "i": 172,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "Then, I'll counter it with my own bazooka!"
 },
 {
  "i": 173,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,0)}Rubber..."
 },
 {
  "i": 174,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "Huh? It won't move!"
 },
 {
  "i": 175,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "My right arm won't move!"
 },
 {
  "i": 176,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "It won't stretch either!"
 },
 {
  "i": 177,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "The absence of pain is the zombie's greatest disadvantage."
 },
 {
  "i": 178,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "He's your shadow..."
 },
 {
  "i": 179,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Finish him off, Luffy."
 },
 {
  "i": 180,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Rubber..."
 },
 {
  "i": 181,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Go!"
 },
 {
  "i": 182,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Take him down, Straw Hat!"
 },
 {
  "i": 183,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Both",
  "text": "Heads up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 184,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Giant..."
 },
 {
  "i": 185,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Bazooka!"
 },
 {
  "i": 186,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "All",
  "text": "He did it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 187,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "No matter what kind of zombie he is, he can't possibly get up after that."
 },
 {
  "i": 188,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Oars lost."
 },
 {
  "i": 189,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "And this time for good."
 },
 {
  "i": 190,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "What's gonna happen to Thriller Bark?"
 },
 {
  "i": 191,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "They did it."
 },
 {
  "i": 192,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "They're quite something."
 },
 {
  "i": 193,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hildon",
  "text": "It seems I brought some dangerous fellas..."
 },
 {
  "i": 194,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "What happened?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 195,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Where's our Master?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 196,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "He won!"
 },
 {
  "i": 197,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "This time he really did it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 198,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "He won!"
 },
 {
  "i": 199,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Thanks a lot!"
 },
 {
  "i": 200,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "You're the best!"
 },
 {
  "i": 201,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "As expected from our ray of hope!"
 },
 {
  "i": 202,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "This man lived up to our expectations after all!"
 },
 {
  "i": 203,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Where's Straw Hat?"
 },
 {
  "i": 204,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "A midget!"
 },
 {
  "i": 205,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Who're you?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 206,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Why did you shrink?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 207,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "It doesn't hurt, and yet, I can't move."
 },
 {
  "i": 208,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "He's still awake, despite having his bones pulverized."
 },
 {
  "i": 209,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "How much more can this power make fun of life."
 },
 {
  "i": 210,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "The morning sun."
 },
 {
  "i": 211,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Why?"
 },
 {
  "i": 212,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "What's this unease I feel...?"
 },
 {
  "i": 213,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Hey, Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 214,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Get your shadow back, quickly!"
 },
 {
  "i": 215,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "There's no time to celebrate!"
 },
 {
  "i": 216,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Everyone here might disappear!"
 },
 {
  "i": 217,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "The shadows!"
 },
 {
  "i": 218,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "He's right! We gotta hurry!"
 },
 {
  "i": 219,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Now, punch that Moriah awake and\\Nmake him return all of our shadows!"
 },
 {
  "i": 220,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "The morning sun has almost risen!"
 },
 {
  "i": 221,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "There's no need..."
 },
 {
  "i": 222,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "to punch me awake."
 },
 {
  "i": 223,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Moriah!"
 },
 {
  "i": 224,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Master!"
 },
 {
  "i": 225,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "I'm glad you're alright!"
 },
 {
  "i": 226,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Moriah-sama would never fall that easily!"
 },
 {
  "i": 227,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "I-It is better now that you're awake!"
 },
 {
  "i": 228,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Now... if you don't wanna get beaten by the Straw Hats again, you better release all of our shadows!"
 },
 {
  "i": 229,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Yes, give 'em back, you bastard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 230,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "This isn't a child's game."
 },
 {
  "i": 231,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "A true pirate can't be threatened with that!"
 },
 {
  "i": 232,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "If you dogs of the forest were behind this,"
 },
 {
  "i": 233,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "That solves the mystery of\\NStraw Hat's excessive power-up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 234,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "It's disturbing to think that\\Nyou took advantage of my shadow ability!"
 },
 {
  "i": 235,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Shut up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 236,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Give back the shadows!"
 },
 {
  "i": 237,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Straw Hat, how dare you destroy my Thriller Bark!?"
 },
 {
  "i": 238,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "You were the one who messed with our trip!"
 },
 {
  "i": 239,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Give back our shadows before the sun rises!"
 },
 {
  "i": 240,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Had you continued on your travels in your\\Ncurrent state, you would have only found death!"
 },
 {
  "i": 241,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "You wouldn't have lasted a minute in the New World!"
 },
 {
  "i": 242,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "You've gathered some impressive subordinates, but..."
 },
 {
  "i": 243,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "you will lose them all!"
 },
 {
  "i": 244,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Do you know why?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 245,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Hey, Straw Hat, this isn't the time to chat!"
 },
 {
  "i": 246,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Look at the sky!"
 },
 {
  "i": 247,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It's getting brighter!"
 },
 {
  "i": 248,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Hurry up and retrieve the shadows!"
 },
 {
  "i": 249,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "There's no time left!"
 },
 {
  "i": 250,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I found the answer from personal experience!"
 },
 {
  "i": 251,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Why did I lose all my skilled subordinates after they made a reputation for themselves!?"
 },
 {
  "i": 252,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I lost my companions because they were alive!"
 },
 {
  "i": 253,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "If they're undead zombies from the very start, then you won't lose them!"
 },
 {
  "i": 254,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Zombies are immortal!"
 },
 {
  "i": 255,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "An unlimited amount of soldiers who can be replaced at any time!"
 },
 {
  "i": 256,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I'll use this undead army to go after the title of Pirate King once more!"
 },
 {
  "i": 257,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "You should be grateful that I chose your shadows to become my subordinates!"
 },
 {
  "i": 258,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Something's stuck to me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 259,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Now!"
 },
 {
  "i": 260,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Hear my words, shadows of Thriller Bark!"
 },
 {
  "i": 261,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Become one with my power!"
 },
 {
  "i": 262,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Asgard: heavenly residence of the gods and slain heroes in Norse mythology"
 },
 {
  "i": 263,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Shadows' Asgard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 264,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Brother!"
 },
 {
  "i": 265,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "His shadow was taken."
 },
 {
  "i": 266,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "The shadows are...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 267,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "No way!"
 },
 {
  "i": 268,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "He's gathering the shadows from the whole island and absorbing them!"
 },
 {
  "i": 269,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Straw Hat!"
 },
 {
  "i": 270,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "You withstood 100 shadows, didn't you?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 271,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Then, I can withstand..."
 },
 {
  "i": 272,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "200!"
 },
 {
  "i": 273,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "300!"
 },
 {
  "i": 274,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "600!"
 },
 {
  "i": 275,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "700!"
 },
 {
  "i": 276,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "1000 shadows!"
 },
 {
  "i": 277,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It's all over."
 },
 {
  "i": 278,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "What is that thing?"
 },
 {
  "i": 279,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I'm back to normal."
 },
 {
  "i": 280,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It's nearly morning!"
 },
 {
  "i": 281,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Even Straw Hat couldn't defeat Oars with 100 shadows."
 },
 {
  "i": 282,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "But 10 times that amount?"
 },
 {
  "i": 283,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "So the original user can withstand a much larger amount?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 284,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "W-We're done for!"
 },
 {
  "i": 285,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "What's gonna happen now?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 286,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "This can't be true!"
 },
 {
  "i": 287,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "He absorbed Straw Hat's shadow too."
 },
 {
  "i": 288,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Run!"
 },
 {
  "i": 289,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We don't stand a chance!"
 },
 {
  "i": 290,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Hey, hey, hey, hey!"
 },
 {
  "i": 291,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "He's breaking the island apart!"
 },
 {
  "i": 292,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "The mast-mansion is coming down!"
 },
 {
  "i": 293,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Run!"
 },
 {
  "i": 294,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Run into the forest!"
 },
 {
  "i": 295,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "This is really it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 296,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "I'm disappearing!"
 },
 {
  "i": 297,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "My body is disappearing!"
 },
 {
  "i": 298,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Someone help me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 299,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Fool! Hurry and get in the shade!"
 },
 {
  "i": 300,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "The sunlight is almost upon us!"
 },
 {
  "i": 301,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Head to the forest through the shade!"
 },
 {
  "i": 302,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Don't leave the mansion's shadow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 303,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Captain Lola!"
 },
 {
  "i": 304,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "What're you doing?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 305,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Hurry up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 306,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "You guys run."
 },
 {
  "i": 307,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "What're you saying?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 308,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "You're coming with us!"
 },
 {
  "i": 309,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "I'm the one who’s responsible..."
 },
 {
  "i": 310,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "for this bet."
 },
 {
  "i": 311,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Look over there."
 },
 {
  "i": 312,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "They..."
 },
 {
  "i": 313,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Those guys..."
 },
 {
  "i": 314,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "They haven't moved an inch."
 },
 {
  "i": 315,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "They were also stripped of their shadows."
 },
 {
  "i": 316,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "No way!"
 },
 {
  "i": 317,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "They still think they can win?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 318,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "But he destroyed half of the island with a single blow."
 },
 {
  "i": 319,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Moriah's power exceeds that of Oars' right now!"
 },
 {
  "i": 320,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Since they haven't given up yet..."
 },
 {
  "i": 321,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "I'm not moving from here."
 },
 {
  "i": 322,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "If we keep calling them our \"Ray of Hope\" and then abandon them at the first sight of trouble,"
 },
 {
  "i": 323,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "we're nothing but a bunch of maggots."
 },
 {
  "i": 324,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "But in our current situation..."
 },
 {
  "i": 325,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "You go ahead and escape."
 },
 {
  "i": 326,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "As your Captain, I promise to uphold your honor."
 },
 {
  "i": 327,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "You just... keep yourselves alive."
 },
 {
  "i": 328,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Captain Lola!"
 },
 {
  "i": 329,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "The light is reaching you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 330,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Hurry and get in the shade!"
 },
 {
  "i": 331,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "It's okay!"
 },
 {
  "i": 332,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "This is what it means to place your hopes in other people!"
 },
 {
  "i": 333,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Captain Lola!"
 },
 {
  "i": 334,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "No way."
 },
 {
  "i": 335,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Do you wanna die?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 336,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Life or death. There's just one answer!"
 },
 {
  "i": 337,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
